Mary-Kate Olsen and Ashley Olsen -LRB- born June 13 , 1986 -RRB- , also known as the Olsen twins collectively , are American fashion designers and former child actresses .
The fraternal twins made their acting debut as infants playing Michelle Tanner on the television series Full House .
At the age of six , Mary-Kate and Ashley Olsen began starring together in TV , film , and video projects , which continued to their teenage years .
Through their company Dualstar , the Olsens joined the ranks of the wealthiest women in the entertainment industry at a young age .